  Configure Terminal Title
  Select which items to display in the terminal title.

  Type to search
  >
› [x] five-hour-limit  Remaining usage on the 5-hour or only usage limit (omitted when unavailabl…
  [x] weekly-limit     Remaining usage on the weekly or secondary usage limit (omitted when unava…
  [ ] app-name         Codex app name
  [ ] project-name     Project name (falls back to current directory name)
  [ ] current-dir      Current working directory
  [ ] activity         Spinner while working, action-required message while blocked.
  [ ] run-state        Compact session run-state text (Ready, Working, Thinking)
  [ ] thread-title     Current thread title, or thread identifier when unnamed

  monthly 65% | weekly 50%
  Press space to toggle; ←/→ to move; enter to confirm and close; esc to close
